  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a pan, add cumin seeds and let them sizzle.",
    "Add chopped green peppers and onions to the pan. Stir-fry until the vegetables are slightly softened.",
    "Stir in tomato puree, salt, garam masala powder, coriander powder, turmeric powder, and red chili powder. Simmer for about 5 minutes.",
    "Add cooked rigatoni to the sauce. Mix well and let it simmer for another 2-3 minutes until all ingredients are heated evenly.",
    "Serve hot with a side of raita or rice."
